      • changeStatus

        public void changeStatus(String newStatus,
                         BindingResult bindingResult)
        Updates driver status. For successful status change, status value should be equal to String representation for any value in DriverStatus enumeration. If status changed to DriverStatus.RESTING, then this method will try to unassign driver from order, if his part is completed.
        Specified by:
